°Plaque 1: 
FILBY
Precious Memories of our Dad and Mum
George A. Filby and Eileen Filby (nee Riddell)
12.12.1924 - 19.01.2012 and 13.09.1927 -26.01.1981
Loving, special Parents, Grand-parents and Great-grandparents
Dear memories too of our lovely Sister, Gail Buchan (nee Filby)
07.021952 10.05.1988 and of others gone before
Always in our hearts
"Ae Fond Kiss, and then we Sever, Ae Fareweel, Alas Forever"

Plaque 2:
Precious Memories of my Brother
Dr. Alan George Filby
10.05.1947 - 15.07.2017
A loving brother to his sister Lynn, his niece Gail, and his nephews Ben, Peter and lain, and his StepMother Joan.
Alan also had a lot of friends in Scotland and England
driving all over the country to see them when he could.
